{
  "stem": "888.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then there was boys, you know, who had different days, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like [? cast. ?] You know, like for instance, one had Monday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One had Tuesday.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Wednesday, sometimes two.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, and then we always had cousins, you know, who were in the yeshiva over there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I had a cousin, of course, you know, who worked with my father in the business.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was a steady-- ate in the house all the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's why I say there was, almost every day there was 14, 15 people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then on holidays it was of course, sometimes-- or Saturdays, even more.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What was the name of the yeshiva in the Satmar?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was the Satmar Yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was the Satmar Rebbe and the Satmar Yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was considered-- in the Orthodox circles, he was a very well known rabbi.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most certainly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I met him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, we used to go to his services, not every Saturday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Occasionally on Saturdays, on high holidays we attended his services.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, even if we didn't attend, you know that we would go to his, you know-- what do you call the tish, the table.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In other words, when, you know-- because there were so many people who ate with him, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then everybody would come after.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After everybody was finished at home, they would come, you know, to the activities-- whatever activities, sometimes dancing, you know, depending what kind of holiday it was, you know, like Passover or Sukkot.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Of course, Simchas Torah it was another situation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because Simchas Torah, everybody attended.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe 1,000 to 2,000 people were dancing in the, in the synagogue, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the rabbi would go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, he would make a-- they make a circle.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
